 (17,1,'a','computer is a electronic device which computes many operations in fraction second.\r\n\r\ncomputer has mainly five blocks:\r\n1.input:it gives inputs to the computer. ex:keyboard\r\n2.output\r\n3.control unit\r\n4.arithemetic logic unit\r\n5.processing unit\r\n ','157','27/Jun/2017','NC',0,'Computer Science'),
 (18,1,'a','Block diagram as shown in the paper,block diagram consists of mainly 3 parts input,cpu,output.input means whatever data we given to the computer.input parts are key board,mouse. cpu means central processing unit,cpu is a brain of the computer it process the data and executing arithmetic logic unit,it is a main part of the computer. processing output means the computer shows or by print.out parts like monitor,printer etc. ','150','27/Jun/2017','NC',0,'Computer Science'),
 (19,1,'a',' computer is a electronic device which computes many operations in fraction of seconds.\r\n\r\ncomputer has mainly classified into five parts:\r\n1.Input:it gives input to the computer.ex:keyboard\r\n2.output\r\n3.control unit\r\n4.arithmatic logic unit\r\n5.processing unit','158','27/Jun/2017','NC',0,'Computer Science'),
 (20,1,'b','HOME MENU IS PRESENT IN THE MS WORD AND IT HAS THE FOLLOWING OPTIONS.\r\n1: CLIP BOARD\r\n2: PARAGRAPH\r\n3: FONT\r\n4: STYLES AND EDITING \r\n\r\n1: CLIP BOARD: IT HAS CUT, COPY, AND PASTE OPTIONS\r\nCUT- TO MOVE THE CONTENT FROM ONE PLACE TO OTHER\r\nCTRL+X IS THE SHORTCUT\r\nCOPY- TO SHARE THE SAME COPY WITH THE OTHER','126','27/Jun/2017','NC',0,'Computer Science');
