 (78,1,'b','Home menu option mainly consists 5 types a)clip board b)font)c)paragraph d)styles e)editing.a)clip board:aa).cut:it use to cut the document(ctrl+x).ab).copy:it use to copy the document(ctrl+v).ac).paste:it use to paste the document(ctrl+p).b)font:ba).underline:it use to selected text to underline(ctrl+u).bb)bold: make the selected text bold(ctrl+b).bc)italic:use to italicize the selected text(ctrl+i).bd)font colour:it use to change the font colour.c)paragraph:ca)align text left:align text to the left(ctrl+l)cb)align text left:align text to the right(ctrl+r).cc)align centre: align text to the centre(ctrl+e).cd)justify: to justify the selected text(ctrl+j).d)styles:it is use to change the shape of the letters.heading01,heading02 etc.e)editing:ea)find:find text in the document.eb)replace:it is use replace text in the document.ec)select: select text in the document. ','150','27/Jun/2017','NC',0,'Computer Science');
