 (585,7,'15','\r\noptions of excel spreadsheet menu bar\r\nthe main menu consists of following options they are \r\n1.clipboard\r\n2.font\r\n3.alignment\r\n4.number \r\n5.styles \r\n6.editing\r\n\r\n1.clipboard\r\n consists of three opions like cut copy and paste can be done on selected cells.\r\n2.font:\r\nfont:to select the font face,\r\nincrese font size ,decrease font size\r\nbold:to write in bold letters and numbers,italic :to write in the cursive manner,underline : to under line the text or symboles or numerical figures,font colour: to change the font colour \r\n3.alignment: to align text and figure in 6 possible ways shown in the box in alignment sub menu. they are \r\nalign to right upper corner to left boottom corner\r\ncdiagonal writing is an option in here. \r\nmerge and center : it merges all the cells and brings them to the center.\r\ncell break is to move to next cell.\r\n\r\n4.Number: this sub menu contains following options.\r\nnumber styles: to choose from variety of numbering styles(notations) like scientific notations, normal numeric,exonetial etc.\r\n\r\nmoney notation:to use the different money notations like $ dollar, rupee, pounds etc\r\n\r\nincrese the decimal digits, \r\ndecrese the decimal digits,\r\npercentage notation,\r\n\r\n\r\nstyles:\r\n5.conditional formating : we have variety of options in this menu where \r\n we can easily colour the cells by certain conditions appied to them\r\nlike we can colour the cells if it has no less than 50. we can put sym\r\n-ols \r\nformate table: to use the designs which is already there.\r\nformate cells:to use the cell designs,\r\n \r\n6.cells: to insert ,delete edit cells.\r\n7.editing:\r\nfind-to find a cell which contains the given text or number.\r\n replace-to replace a figure by another.\r\nsort-to sort the cells according to requirement.\r\n\r\n\r\n  \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n','135','01/Jul/2017','NC',0,'Computer Science'),
 (586,7,'15','\r\n1.Office botton : \r\na.New    : It is used to create a new document.         \r\nb.Open  : It is used to open existing document.\r\nc.Save   : It is used to save the document.\r\nSave As          \r\n    d.Print      \r\n    e.Prepare \r\n    f.Send             \r\n    g.Publish \r\n    h.Close     \r\n                         \r\nPrint preview:\r\n   1.Print\r\n     a.Print\r\n     b.Options                  \r\n     2. Page setup               \r\n     a.Margins\r\n     b.Orientation       \r\n     c.Size                     \r\n  3.Zoom                         \r\n     a.Zoom\r\n     b.100%                  \r\n     c.One page          \r\n     d.Two page          \r\n     e.Page width        \r\n 4.Preview                      \r\n     a.Show ruler\r\n     b.Magnifier            \r\n     c.Shrink one page \r\n     d.Next page            \r\n     e.Previous page    \r\n','153','01/Jul/2017','NC',0,'Computer Science');
