 (590,7,'16','Filter-This option is used to filter the particular data .\r\n\r\nSort - Sort the data according to alphabeticatal or numerics formate etc.\r\n\r\ncut  - To cut the content in the document.\r\n\r\ncopy - To copy the content of the document.\r\n\r\npaste- This option will paste the content from one place to other place\r\n \r\nin the sheet.\r\n\r\npaste special- This option is used to paste the formula or text from one \r\ncell to other \r\n\r\ncell or from column to column.Add comment-This option is used to add a comment to a\r\n \r\nparticular cell in the sheet.\r\n\r\nInsert cell-This option is used to insert the column or row in the sheet.\r\nDelet:To delet the selected cell.\r\nRename:To rename the working sheet of the document.\r\n\r\n','127','01/Jul/2017','NC',0,'Computer Science'),
