 (598,7,'15','The various menu options in Excel are\r\n\r\nHome\r\nInsert\r\nPage Layout\r\nData\r\nFormulas\r\nReview\r\nView\r\n\r\nHome Menu\r\n1)Clip Board\r\na)Cut-Used to cut the selected data.\r\nb)copy-Used to copy the selected data.\r\nc)paste-Used to paste the data.\r\n\r\n2)Font\r\na)font-to select required font style.\r\nb)font size-to select required font size.\r\nc)font colour-to select required font colour.\r\nd)Increase or decrease font size\r\ne)fill colour\r\nF)bold-to make the text bold \r\ng)italics-to make the text italicised\r\nh)underline-to underline the text\r\n\r\n3)Alignment\r\na)top align-to align terxt to the top of the cell\r\nb)middle align-align text in middle of the cell\r\nc)bottom align-align text at the bottom of the cell\r\nd)right align-align text to the right\r\ne)left align-align text to the left\r\nf)centre align-align text to the centre\r\ng)orientation-to change the direction of the text\r\nf)merge and center-To merge cells and place the contents at the centre\r\n\r\n4)styles\r\na)conditional formatting-To format the data in the cells\r\nb)format as table-to apply a ready made table to the data entered\r\nc)cell styles-to change the styles of the cells\r\n\r\n5)number\r\na)% style-to add %symbol to the data\r\nb)comma style-to enter numerous data separated by commas\r\nc)increase decimal-to add zeros\r\nd)decrease decimal-to decrease the number of zeros\r\ne)accounting number format\r\nf)number format\r\n\r\n6)cells\r\na)insert-to insert new cells \r\nb)delete-to delete the cells\r\nc)format-to format all the cells\r\n\r\n7)editing\r\na)sum\r\nb)fill\r\nc)clear\r\nd)sort and filter\r\ne)find and replace\r\n\r\n\r\nInsert Menu\r\n\r\n1)tables\r\na)Pivot table\r\nb)table\r\n\r\n2)Illustrations\r\na)Picture\r\nb)ClipArt\r\nc)Shapes\r\nd)SmartArt\r\n\r\n3))Charts\r\na)Column\r\nb)Line\r\nc)Pie\r\nd)Bar\r\ne)Area\r\n\r\n4)links\r\na)Hyperlinks\r\n\r\n5)text\r\na)TextBox\r\nb)header&footer\r\nc)WordArt\r\nd)Object\r\ne)Symbol\r\n\r\n\r\nPage layout Menu\r\n1)theme\r\na)themes\r\nb)colour\r\nc)font\r\nd)effects\r\n\r\n2)Page Setup\r\na)Margin\r\nb)Size\r\nc)Orientation\r\nd)Print Area\r\ne)background\r\n\r\n\r\n','149','01/Jul/2017','NC',0,'Computer Science');
