 (600,7,'15','Home menu:a)clip board b)font c)alignment.aa)cut: this option is used to cut the document(ctrl+x).ab)copy: this option is used to copy the document(ctrl+c).paste: this option is used to paste the document(ctrl+v).ba)italic: to italicize the content of the document.bb)bold: it is used to make selected content bold.bc)underline: it is used to underline the selected content.painter: it is used to paint the selected content.ca)left alignment:it is used to selected text to move left side(ctrl+l).cb)right alignment:it is used to selected text to move right side(ctrl+r).cc)centre alignment:it is used to selected text centre(ctrl+e).2.Insert menu:a)table b)illustration c)charts d)links.aa)pivot table: it is used to summarize the data.table: this option is used to insert the table.ba)shapes: it is used to uses the circle,rectangle some other other type shapes.bb)clip art: it is used to attach the include movie drawing etc.bc)smart art:it is used graphic,visually communicate.ca) in chart option we are use pie chart,line graph,column chart etc.da)hyper links: this option is used to create a link to a web page.3.Page lay out:a)themes b)conditional formating c)margines d)print area e)size f)width g)print area.a)themes:this option is used to take colours, fonts etc.b)conditional formatting: this option is used to highlights to the content document.c)margins: it is used to change the margines.d)print area) this option is used to some changes to the pages.e)size: it is use to change size of sheet.f)this option is used to change to width of the sheet.g)print area: it is used to some changes to the page before print. \r\n\r\n','150','01/Jul/2017','NC',0,'Computer Science'),
