 (609,7,'15','There are 7 submenus are there in exel.Namely \r\n1)Home\r\n2)Insert\r\n3)Page layout \r\n4)Formulas \r\n5)Data \r\n6)Preview \r\n7)view\r\n1)HOME : In this sub menu we can perform various operations.It contains vrious options.these are explained bellow.\r\nclipboard: it contains a)cut-is used to replace the data\r\n       b)copy-used to copy the selected data\r\n       c)paste- used to paste the data at desired place.\r\n\r\nFont: in this we can increase font size , decrease font size ,change font colour, underline,bold,italics etc options will be performed.\r\nAllignment: tex allignment in the box will be performed.allign text at right ,left ,allign at top,bottom,middle.\r\nCells-by using this option we can insert ,delete ,format the cells\r\n        Numbers-we can select the various number sistems by using this option.\r\n2)INSERT:by using this option we can add/insert \r\n         a)tables\r\n         b) illustrations:pictures,clipart,smart art , shapes etc.\r\n         c)text:header,footer  etc\r\n  to the work sheet.\r\n3)PAGE LAYOUT: a) themes-we can add various themes,\r\n               b)page setup-page will be designed as we needed, margins ,orientations,page breaks will be performed.\r\n               \r\n4)VIEW:ZOOM\r\n\r\n','147','01/Jul/2017','NC',0,'Computer Science'),
