 (664,7,'15','\r\nThe options in the Excel File are as follows\r\n       1.HOME: This option contains the following options they are\r\n       (a)CLIPBOARD:It contains CUT-To cut the content, COPY-Copy the desired content.\r\n       (b)FONT:It contains the options fro the font size,option for changing the font face font color\r\n       (c)ALIGNMENT: is used for aligning thetext in the cells to the middle,left and right.\r\n       (d)NUMBER: It shows the number tab of the format cells dialogue box.\r\n       (e)STYLES\r\n       2.INSERT: used for inserting the picture, shape,smart arts, and charts like bar chart,column, line,pie, area\r\n       3.PAGE LAYOUT:used for inserting the themes.\r\n       4.FORMULAS: It is used for inserting the various maths formulae.\r\n       5.DATA:\r\n\r\n','143','01/Jul/2017','NC',0,'Computer Science'),
